<h3><span style="font-weight: 400;"><img src="https://s.w.org/images/core/emoji/15.0.3/72x72/2699.png" alt="âš™" class="wp-smiley" style="height: 1em; max-height: 1em;" /></span><span style="font-weight: 400;">How to Set RSI in MetaTrader 4 (MT4)</span></h3>
<p><span style="font-weight: 400;">Setting up RSI in </span><a href="https://www.atfx.com.bz/en/trading-platforms/metatrader-4" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><span style="font-weight: 400;">MT4</span></a><span style="font-weight: 400;"> is simple and quick. Follow these steps:</span></p>
<ol>
